snippet.title: ReThinkingTourism
snippet.description:
ReThinkingTourism is Doug Lansky's commentary on the travel industry, looking at trends, strategies, sustainability, marketing and master plans for destinations, hotels, airlines, airport and other key stakeholders. The goal is to be insightful, irreverent, intelligent and entertaining.

Doug Lansky is a keynote speaker and advisor for the tourism industry. He has spoken for Google Travel, Microsoft, Amadeus, Expedia, Booking.com as well as airports, hotel associations and city, regional, state and national Destination Marketing Organizations around the world from Singapore to South Dakota to Stockholm.
